{"tid":529013,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Intel警告使用舊款處理器的用戶：更新或導致PC無限重啟！","createTime":"2018-01-14T12:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T06:45:01.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"51b1757b7ae9ed8948279e06c9b4a6fb38af957c","tid":529013,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:35:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://pc3mag.com/intel-broadwell-haswell-pc-restart/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fintel-broadwell-haswell-pc-restart%2F&d=n17qn7TJDXoHaR3Der2I%2FJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=c7a1cc22\" target=\"_blank\">https://pc3mag.com/intel-broadwell-haswell-pc-restart/</a><br />\n<br />\n日前intel表示，最近發佈的安全更新，或會導致部分舊款處理器，會出現頻繁重啟的情況，當中包括2015年推出的Broadwell和2013年以前的Haswell處理器，而影響的包括個人電腦與商用伺服器。intel數據中心部門總經理Navin Shenoy，指已經接到客戶反應這問題的存在，而公司正在積極解決這問題，包括已迅速與這些客戶一起診斷，以解決無限重新更新的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pc3mag.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/20160127-intel-superbowl-city-100646139-orig_pc3leo-compressed-768x512.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F20160127-intel-superbowl-city-100646139-orig_pc3leo-compressed-768x512.jpg&h=80d3b400&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"07e3d86375e77fb4a731ee02ebda4678f275f3b3","tid":529013,"uid":37820,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:40:35.000Z","msg":"Intel i5 三代 轉會用ryzen 7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e903041df37c1b2a283efda0c67743f809e8c0c","tid":529013,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:42:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e529f40b84139930f3dfccd8208e884b422291fe","tid":529013,"uid":82829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:43:43.000Z","msg":"pentium g2030<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d80102fde9a2161670